{"type": "article", "id": 10896, "title": "The Mason Watch 大理石手表系列", "description": "", "date": "2015-06-17T07:15:13Z", "super_tag": "", "tags": [], "category": 25, "column": 28, "author": 1329, "comment_count": 1, "praise_count": 58, "image": "img/article/article_show/201606061358039lhyouvb6dFA3iRc.jpg", "contents": "\n\n<p>\r\n\t由美国设计师 Lorenzo Buffa 主理的手表品牌 Analog Watch Co. 最近推出了一款大理石质感的 The Mason Watch 手表系列。手表采用天然大理石材质以精细手工打磨而成，表带内里配合皮革设计，耐用之余又能融合自然简约之美。大理石最吸引人的部分在于它源自上万年的地壳自然运转的沉积，每一块都独一无二。目前，The Mason Watch 正在 Kickstarter 上众筹，起售价 165 美元（约合人民币 1025 元），表盘提供圆形与六边形两种选择，<a href=\"https://www.kickstarter.com/projects/analogwatchco/the-mason-watch-an-innovative-solid-marble-timepie\" target=\"_blank\">点击这里尝试购买</a>。\r\n</p>\r\n<p>\r\n\t</p>\n<p style=\"text-align:center;\">\r\n\t\t<img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135800cC5s1EBVMyiP0qFb.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"1.0\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135801dcsRC9Ag8FMS1f6x.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.70441176\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/201606061358017u5Kiz3aRhLkgESv.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135801gkC0xdGW5b6LfBX2.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.66617647\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135802BDu0O9Nkm7x6Jqza.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.56323529\" data-format=\"jpeg\"><img src=\"img/uploads/20160606135802A4m7CWnkUcO0gqlE.jpg\" title=\"3\" alt=\"3\" data-ratio=\"0.75\" data-format=\"jpeg\">\r\n\t</p>\r\n\r\n<div>\r\n\t<br>\r\n</div>\n\n\n"}